===Noun===
'''fission'''
#The [[process]] whereby one item splits to become two.
#{{physics}}: The process of splitting an [[atom]] into smaller [[particle]]s.
#{{biology}}: The process by which a [[bacterium]] splits to form two [[daughter]] [[cell]]s.

